<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MiRestcon IA — Conversa con tu restaurante</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Pedidos, cocina, inventario, reportes — todo con una conversación. La IA para restaurantes peruanos.">
  <link href="/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/vendor/bootstrap-icons/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #F0F2F8; color: #0a0f24;
      color: #fff;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ---- HERO ---- */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 60px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(255,107,53,0.13) 0%, transparent 70%),
                  #0a0f24;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,53,0.35);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #FF6B35;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 52px);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #fff;
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .hero-title span {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B35, #fd9931);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 20px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fefbf5, #fd9931, #df2c05);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 15px 32px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: none;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255,107,53,0.35);
    }

    .btn-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(255,107,53,0.5);
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-cta-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: transparent;
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 2px solid #FF6B35;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-cta-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,107,53,0.1);
      color: #FF6B35;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .hero-social-proof {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .hero-social-proof strong {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }

    /* ---- OLD MODEL ---- */
    .section-old {
      background: #0d1229;
      padding: 96px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-label {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #fff;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto 56px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .old-cards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
    }

    .old-card {
      background: #141828;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .old-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .old-card-icon {
      font-size: 36px;
      opacity: 0.5;
      filter: grayscale(1);
    }

    .old-card-name {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }

    .old-card-desc {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .old-card-x {
      position: absolute;
      top: 14px;
      right: 14px;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background: rgba(220,53,69,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #dc3545;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .old-message {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 28px);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.3;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .old-message span {
      color: #FF6B35;
    }

    /* ---- FEATURES ---- */
    .section-features {
      background: #0a0f24;
      padding: 96px 20px;
    }

    .section-features .inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .features-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: #141828;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #FF6B35;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .feature-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .feature-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ---- SEARCH ---- */
    .section-search {
      background: #f5f6fa;
      padding: 96px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-search .section-title {
      color: #0a0f24;
    }

    .section-search .section-subtitle {
      color: rgba(10,15,36,0.55);
    }

    .search-wrap {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    .search-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px 24px 18px 52px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(10,15,36,0.12);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      background: #fff;
      color: #0a0f24;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .search-input:focus {
      border-color: #FF6B35;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
    }

    .search-input::placeholder {
      color: rgba(10,15,36,0.35);
    }

    .search-icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 20px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: rgba(10,15,36,0.4);
      font-size: 20px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .search-dropdown {
      position: absolute;
      top: calc(100% + 8px);
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(10,15,36,0.1);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(10,15,36,0.15);
      overflow: hidden;
      z-index: 100;
      display: none;
    }

    .search-dropdown.active {
      display: block;
    }

    .search-item {
      padding: 14px 22px;
      text-align: left;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #0a0f24;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,15,36,0.06);
      transition: background 0.12s;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .search-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .search-item:hover {
      background: rgba(255,107,53,0.06);
    }

    .search-item-icon {
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .search-item-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(10,15,36,0.4);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .search-loading {
      padding: 16px 22px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(10,15,36,0.4);
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ---- VOICES ---- */
    .section-voices {
      padding: 96px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f24 0%, #141828 100%);
    }
    .section-voices .inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .voices-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .voices-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .voices-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .voice-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all .3s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .voice-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.4);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(255,107,53,0.15);
    }
    .voice-avatar {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .voice-avatar.aoede {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d 0%, #c44dd9 100%);
    }
    .voice-avatar.kore {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #4b3cc4 100%);
    }
    .voice-avatar.puck {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
    }
    .voice-name {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .voice-type {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .voice-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .voice-hint {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .voices-cta-wrap {
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ---- PLANS ---- */
    .section-plans {
      background: #0d1229;
      padding: 96px 20px;
    }

    .section-plans .inner {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .plans-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .plans-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .plans-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 380px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
    }

    .plan-card {
      background: #141828;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 36px 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .plan-card.featured {
      border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.4);
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255,107,53,0.08) 0%, #141828 60%);
    }

    .plan-card.featured::before {
      content: 'MÁS POPULAR';
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B35, #fd9931);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .plan-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    .plan-price {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .plan-price span {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .plan-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .plan-features {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .plan-features li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .plan-features li i {
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-size: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .plan-btn {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 13px 24px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    }

    .plan-btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .plan-btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .plan-btn-orange {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B35, #fd9931);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(255,107,53,0.3);
    }

    .plan-btn-orange:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(255,107,53,0.45);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .plans-see-all {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .plans-see-all a {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .plans-see-all a:hover {
      color: #FF6B35;
    }

    /* ---- FINAL CTA ---- */
    .section-final-cta {
      background: #0a0f24;
      padding: 120px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .section-final-cta::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 700px;
      height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(255,107,53,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .final-cta-title {
      font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 52px);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #fff;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .final-cta-title span {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B35, #fd9931);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .final-cta-sub {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    /* ---- DIVIDER ---- */
    .divider-glow {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,107,53,0.3), transparent);
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ---- RESPONSIVE tweaks ---- */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .old-cards-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .btn-cta, .btn-cta-secondary {
        font-size: 15px;
        padding: 13px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../partials/public-header') %>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="hero">
  <img src="/isotipo.png" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(255,107,53,0.25);" alt="DallIA">

  <div class="hero-label">
    <i class="bi bi-stars"></i>
    DallIA — Tu IA de restaurante
  </div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    DEJA DE OPERAR <span>SOFTWARE.</span><br>
    CONVERSA CON TU RESTAURANTE.
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-subtitle">
    Pedidos, cocina, inventario, reportes —<br>todo con una conversación.
  </p>

  <a href="/auth/google" class="btn-cta">
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink:0;">
      <path d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z" fill="#fff" opacity=".9"/>
      <path d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z" fill="#fff" opacity=".9"/>
      <path d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l2.85-2.22.81-.62z" fill="#fff" opacity=".9"/>
      <path d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z" fill="#fff" opacity=".9"/>
    </svg>
    Probar gratis con Google
  </a>

  <p class="hero-social-proof">
    <strong>50+ restaurantes</strong> en Perú ya lo usan · Sin tarjeta de crédito
  </p>
</section>

<div class="divider-glow"></div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     EL VIEJO MODELO
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="section-old">
  <span class="section-label">El problema</span>
  <h2 class="section-title">El viejo modelo<br>te está frenando</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Mientras sigues usando esto, tu competencia ya conversa con su restaurante.</p>

  <div class="old-cards-grid">
    <div class="old-card">
      <div class="old-card-x">✕</div>
      <div class="old-card-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="old-card-name">Excel</div>
      <div class="old-card-desc">Columnas, fórmulas rotas y datos de hace 3 semanas</div>
    </div>
    <div class="old-card">
      <div class="old-card-x">✕</div>
      <div class="old-card-icon">💬</div>
      <div class="old-card-name">WhatsApp</div>
      <div class="old-card-desc">Pedidos mezclados con memes y audios sin escuchar</div>
    </div>
    <div class="old-card">
